Package: DIFseq
Type: Package
Title: Differential Inference for Single-cell RNA-sequencing data
Version: 0.99.1
Author: Fangda Song <songfangda@cuhk.edu.cn>, Yingying Wei <ywei@cuhk.edu.hk>
Maintainer: Fangda Song <songfangda@cuhk.edu.cn>
Description:
    DIFferential Inference for Single-cell RNA-sequencing Data (DIFseq) is an interpretable Bayesian hierarchical model to rigorously quantify the condition effects on both cellular compositions and cell-type-specific gene expression levels for scRNA-seq data.
